---
/**
 * Corporate CTA Section
 *
 * User problem (Corporate): "We need maintenance services for our company."
 * Goal: Capture B2B leads through inquiry form.
 * Visual: Single focused card/CTA with clear action.
 */
---

<section class="bg-bg-section">
  <div class="container-page py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border-default bg-bg-surface px-8 py-12 md:px-16 md:py-16">
      <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-xl text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary-50 text-primary-600" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 22V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v18Z"/>
            <path d="M6 12H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2"/>
            <path d="M18 9h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"/>
            <path d="M10 6h4"/>
            <path d="M10 10h4"/>
            <path d="M10 14h4"/>
            <path d="M10 18h4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="mt-5 text-h3 text-text-primary">Butuh Layanan untuk Perusahaan?</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary text-pretty max-w-md mx-auto">
          Kami menyediakan maintenance rutin, outsourcing teknisi, dan SLA khusus untuk kebutuhan bisnis Anda.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/corporate"
          class="mt-8 inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md border-2 border-primary-500 px-8 text-body font-semibold text-primary-600 transition-all duration-150 ease-out hover:bg-primary-50 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-primary-500"
        >
          Ajukan Inquiry
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
